reviews.review_text: box set..!!!! these shows kicked ass!!! i was at these shows with my friend marc the boys where on fire...they had the sound down by this part of the tour...these shows need to be in dicks picks..they need to made in a box set...even with jerry and bobby getting in to it on stage the next night these shows still kicked ass..jerry sounded good at this time..vince was coming along great at this ponit...the dead had there sound down by this time..it was a great year..i think it was the dead last great year??

Anyone else remember the June Bugs? They were everywhere!  If you stood under a light they'd fall on you, Jerry was spitting them out as the fans were blowing them into their faces!

It was crazy!
